snippet.title: Debunking Flat Earth. Brains Logic Fails Again
snippet.description:
How many more times is Brian going to mess up? It really is not difficult to get an elevation height of Blackpool tower. It really isn't difficult to measure the distance between Dow crag and Blackpool tower... Google earth does it for you. It really is not good enough, after a year, of still not being able to to the line on the top of the tower and extend it to Dow crag to see the result. Brian, your are now in my dishonest category, because I struggle to believe someone can be either so incredibly stupid or so incredibly inept, not in this day and age.
